[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Addressing Hadoop issues**\n\nI need to figure out a fix for the failure related to JAAS Subject.getSubject not being supported on JDK. The Hadoop FileSystem’s local implementation uses UGI, and I'm wondering if there's an alternative feature that doesn’t involve the FileSystem. I could potentially set hadoop.security.authentication to simple. However, I'm facing challenges, especially with the need for a stable public API and testing without using the FileSystem. So, I might explore how to use YarnClient without starting a network.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_07e31b86b05c3a460169fecf65ec4c81a3bc5347dd42de9aa7\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_s9snROe9xtZBclomNfx3KzazAnR0buHEcTsmW59Lty5u-RgTzYkUqRBz30JkCpEDli7g2oDQMjt9gjrH0lQZxFc0ZaMhevf-buwL-6CD6lX7G6AYc_scRDIo0nEqiay43FA3g6s9kRwdZ2Pnk1mzV_olGu1ifRLclvARb_GKSVkgnXPsbtZD5xdNCavh-krQHiXIv5PiRrndpcLLxp2Y7ChyHt4Hf8qLcK_9JZPRO-ePvfRPyKqhKWyBqghLApSO-OciZ2vdOSnBkBL9UdUxvxmR6KBELC4YDxyv_yNpuxAMRTGEwF_iih1EUe9mnkNASWox7hMNJi5RbNAeWCGT6zSGLOtGulr3sDlOr6tmLk30U_pedGtS_33gQGRSjDGUEY8ZlA03mzI_TJTOIWPNewSO0S8GLgOF1-KNrq3COBmgWRzqgI4pBVYAM3EJxkP_V3BmXw8E_BhZtd0Yn9tLJNFohLwPm3VcMXOLv4F5GmcEps5zLJVNh8Hd0SU1XwR0QYdOmXgmmxKR4unvjO3AwuCWCTIs8IKHcnEPJ0MvvCQz4TeQFiDOfbWT6cKYt5gK911NhTpWiG3RzskM2a8keWF2Y9qbHB5kpcr5PrhwuLuBCoIscQknZbzNv0xGgO29nvFRrvIUXvzZGYxyu3P4FGsoKNmh2GPZyXk3k7zHmHMjOeT20i41Ty2FbCcLdi7jVNuUgBe6qMurM5VUdo3nkjNd6dKS3RcT2Re-oa7RwHd8pq3HTxG2AWcrCGVFav7gQgu46abVKNBDnam2j8HRvfyVlsrpuTDppWjyKvnSy-8NhsrX9JGsVPsGH9fh0duIMSVhTajBc0pOpbo79YY2l4IyLi0ZsDgwwqb7peNiHyNqnr8lwDQzMp057D4NvKu3GzPQqCyPSI1WfPBC3kYYDDh0AnSQsNIU-WjAqMi8un14dRd10F6aTzDLgG8kMFUYSEkVQEbi0fRAeZRmZj-pL0aInbNbKn5YdWTl3hom-Fs-Ttyf7nRgWSnYapcn5as3DmTnXm5og7mIlYX1YDfgTFVnB2nVf6JSSSZ-Et3UB_7ofEET_F0fD_KgwRqquDu_5y0vX3ZbF_-Bx4xZ8HNAwR5L6nr-P0XMa8gUMKoRulOTM8ly9hUUxDJJC-NJOgARq-Z4q5z39cRW7XVXLphZ764jqDezY0cC_6Jl-OiojFlR_MmiLmBoe3